{"tid":1616303,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［共識］大家真係想攬炒定只係得把口?","createTime":"2019-10-03T11:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T12:58:39.000Z","uid":165869,"like":119,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a325c483cf08ca54194cd0a9459923c1c36dda19","tid":1616303,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:04:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔知大家仲記唔記得要同佢攬炒嘅初心?<br />\n<br />\nIF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US.<br />\n<br />\n呢句只係一句口號，係講笑定真係抱住一齊死嘅決心?<br />\n<br />\n共軍來了我返歸嘅宗旨你又能唔能夠做到?<br />\n<br />\n反正我會不斷上Twitter推po，等全世界都知道香港準備行緊急法，等啲企業撤出香港，等全球制裁香港政府同中國。<br />\n<br />\n順便做返個民意調查，俾大家一個共識聽日係要去立法會阻佢開會定我哋留喺屋企睇電視食花生。<br />\n<br />\n希望今晚九點前投票完畢，然後大家落街將個消息講俾各區街坊知。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RxDaOa1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRxDaOa1.gif&h=d50fca17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔阻止佢開會，快啲行緊急法攬炒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阻佢老尾，絕對唔可以俾佢用緊急法"},{"pid":"215a8ee38b4494bc0511d3bdf7de54a41d578f48","tid":1616303,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"支持攬炒第一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f8be7969d363f119c2be26672708c067d910cf","tid":1616303,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"支持攬炒嘅順便留個名推po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808b07e5a742eee0bbf07a201a33e187821b1f8d","tid":1616303,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"唔支持攬炒嘅都希望麻煩你講下你嘅意見同睇法，睇下係因為咩顧慮而反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79324cbcab227d34a23dee2195fd28af9d1abaaa","tid":1616303,"uid":98431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4